{"tid":2426268,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"將軍澳電視城內 美術部員工遭佈景板擊中頭受傷","createTime":"2021-02-28T03:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T04:20:38.000Z","uid":239336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c4d2bd5a68998b7eaf44f0bda507b07908af79","tid":2426268,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"將軍澳電視城發生工業意外，早上8時27分，保安員報警指有人工作期間由高處墮下。救護員接報到場將一名姓陳54歲男子送院，現場消息稱他是道具組人員，一度暈眩，其後已回復清醒。警方調查後初步認為無可疑，相信傷者因工受傷，將案轉列「工業意外」處理，目前仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n無綫企業傳訊部回應事件時表示，4名美術部置景組同事於早上8時15分，在錄影廠內拆卸一塊大型佈景板時，固定佈景板之鐵線突然斷開，其中一位同事因而被佈景板撞到，頭部受傷，報警後由救護車送往將軍澳醫院治理，傷者送院時清醒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210228/2WTG2ZUORZH2PJRWGYZ2QZKTNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210228%2F2WTG2ZUORZH2PJRWGYZ2QZKTNI%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3jBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=545ed0b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210228%2F2WTG2ZUORZH2PJRWGYZ2QZKTNI%2F&h=e67c265d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210228/2WTG2ZUORZH2PJRWGYZ2QZKTNI/</a>"},{"pid":"bc8998dd45c46a2bde01daf04ac500a07613d6a3","tid":2426268,"uid":211827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"好邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a3ea62e234936bad1ba62494cea4a3f916ff98","tid":2426268,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"好猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f8a121f887f21ed5a4c29a276a7be7cad958ce","tid":2